                      ],
                      "text": "Relationships",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 6998,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/24/237301566/0ed9af441ff862c8caccc8ba87d3f4e8_3382131558213222413.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Повелители Ночного Ветра",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Sanhaj Kompore was a famous storyteller and the tribe's Border Master. The most powerful Border Masters can expand the borders of the Night Kingdom, and temporarily manifest part of it in the real world. Sanhaj foresaw the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7089,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/29/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_5671433247808590288.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Khaenri'ahn cataclysm",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", so he began to weave a great net of lies, to turn the stacks of woven scrolls into a veil, so as to hide a past that should not again be touched. Sanhaj was disliked by many because he often bet against people from other tribes and deceived them.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Mare Jivari",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "During the Cataclysm, Sanhaj summoned a miniature Night Kingdom and exploded it to defeat the encroaching dark calamity. The battlefield was reduced to a desolate wasteland and became known as the Mare Jivari. Sanhaj and Tenoch, the leader of the tribal coalition forces, gave their lives to activate this spell.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7490,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Теноч",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Although Sanhaj foresaw his and Tenoch's end in the Battle of the Mare Jivari, he joined him to fight the Abyss.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Mahamba",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "An Iktomisaurus, Sanhaj's companion. Sanhaj Kompore was born silent, and the tribal elder said that half of his soul had been lost in the night flames. To seek his missing self, Sanhaj went to the barren land of stone as a child, and only the enigmatic Mahamba agreed to accompany him.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7079,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/19/70239714/d28eded09506620ab178fc3bb1cb7dea_3891656968977458900.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Оророн",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A hero of Natlan who participated in",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7472,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Хаборим",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "'s plan. He is the heir of the Ancient Name Bidii.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Conulaf",
